1. Juče sam *srela* moju staru drugaricu u parku. (Yesterday, I *met* my old friend in the park.)
2. Nadam se da ću *sresti* svog omiljenog pevača na koncertu. (I hope I'll *encounter* my favorite singer at the concert.)
3. Nisam sigurna kada ću *sresti* svog šefa. (I'm not sure when I'll *run into* my boss.)
4. *Sreo* sam ga juče na ulici, ali nisam imao vremena da popričam s njim. (I *ran into* him on the street yesterday, but I didn't have time to talk to him.)
5. Kada se budemo *sreli*, podseti me da ti pozajmim knjigu. (When we *meet*, remind me to lend you a book.)
6. Ako se *sretnemo* u gradu, idemo na kafu. (If we *bump into each other* in the city, let's go for a coffee.)
7. Očekujem da ću *sresti* mnogo novih ljudi na putovanju. (I expect to *meet* many new people on the trip.)
8. Našli smo se na istom seminaru i tamo smo se *sreli*. (We met each other at the same seminar and that's where we *encountered* each other.)